MENINGITIS, MENINGOCOCCAL - GHANA
*********************************
A ProMED-mail post
See Also
Meningitis, meningococcal - West Africa (02) 970328212131
Meningitis, meningococcal - West Africa (03) 970412205719
Meningitis, meningococcal - West Africa (04) 970502140404
Meningitis, meningococcal - West Africa: Correction 970422104300
Meningitis, meningococcal? - Burkina Faso 970131144055
Meningitis, meningococcal? - Ghana, Mali 970131144049
Date: Thu, 22 Jan 1998
From: Dorothy Preslar <dpreslar@fas.org>
Source: Ghana News Agency, 22 Jan 1998

The official news agency of Ghana reports 6 meningitis deaths in the Upper
West region of Ghana, and 3 deaths in the Upper East area.
According to a senior public health officer in the Upper West, health
centres in the region now have sufficient vaccines for those who were not
vaccinated during last year's major outbreak.
--
