e-mail: promed@usa.healthnet.org
[This time last year ProMED-mail reported on a major outbreak of
meningococcal meningitis in West Africa, including Ghana (see citations
above). A major immunization campaign was said to be part of the response
at that time. We would appreciate additional information should
significant numbers of cases begin to accumulate again this year. - Mod.ES
